Notes: Wes got a layup from Gaffney with :06.8 left to take a 62-61 lead. SJC got up
court & Wes knocked ball OOB under the basket w/:01.5 left. SJC got ball in to
Parent and her layup try was blocked by LaCroce, who grabbed reb. as time ran
out. SJC led by as many as 10 (51-41) in 2nd half.
